LORA DEVELOPPMENT
by USYD

The LORA based IoT application project

The project that will be intoduced in this thesis is an IOT network project which the LoRa, BLE and Sub-G involved. The data will be gathered bu the Sensor and anchors which is connected to a BLE module, Sub-G module or LoRa module directly.

MSc PhD Belgrade, MIEEE FIEAust MAAEE ARC Laureate Fellow Director of the Telecommunications Laboratory School of Electrical and Information Engineering The University of Sydney

Joe Peng
